        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When enabled, after you modify the settings of the tabs, all markdown files that opened will automatically refresh when you close the settings panel. If disabled, the changes will not take effect immediately on the Tabs in opened markdown file, and you will need to re-render them matually.",
          "target": "启用后，修改标签页设置后，关闭设置面板时所有已打开的 Markdown 文件将自动刷新。如果禁用，更改不会立即在已打开 Markdown 文件的标签页中生效，您需要手动重新渲染它们。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
