        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "It's just a decorative setting. If you turn on it, you can still control the cursor into tabs to edit the source code.",
          "target": "这只是一个装饰性设置。如果开启，您仍然可以控制光标进入标签页以编辑源代码。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Show tabs nav at the top, bottom, left or right.",
          "target": "在顶部、底部、左侧或右侧显示标签页导航。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Show tabs nav in one line or multiple lines. Only works when the position is 'top' or 'bottom'",
          "target": "在单行或多行中显示标签页导航。仅当位置为“顶部”或“底部”时有效"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "If set true, tab title will be limited to the width of the tab. Otherwise, the tab title will be displayed the full width.",
          "target": "如果设置为 true，标签页标题将被限制在标签页的宽度内。否则，标签页标题将以全宽显示。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "The padding of tabs contents. You can set one to four values(same as css padding). For example, \"0\" means no padding. \"10px\" means 10 pixels on all sides. \"10px 20px\" means 10 pixels on top and bottom, 20 pixels on left and right.Not only \"px\" but also \"em\", \"rem\" and other units are supported.",
          "target": "标签页内容的内边距。您可以设置一到四个值（与 CSS padding 相同）。例如，“0”表示无内边距。“10px”表示所有边 10 像素。“10px 20px”表示上下 10 像素，左右 20 像素。不仅支持“px”，还支持“em”、“rem”和其他单位。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "If a feasible CSS size is set (for example, 250px, 15em, 50vh, etc.), then when the height of the tabs reaches this size, the excess part can be scrolled. Note that the value should not be set too small, otherwise the tabs will not display properly.",
          "target": "如果设置了可行的 CSS 尺寸（例如，250px、15em、50vh 等），那么当标签页的高度达到此尺寸时，超出部分可以滚动。请注意，值不应设置得太小，否则标签页将无法正常显示。"
